pipit
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:a small, brown, ground-nesting bird, Anthus novaeseelandiae (also called ground (or native) lark, kataitai, pihoihoi).
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
